&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ARE YOU INTERESTED IN TROPICAL MEDICINE, INFECTIOUS DISEASE AND CYSTIC FIBROSIS?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;John Warin Ward provides specialist care in Tropical medicine, infectious disease . We are a 16 bedded department, all side rooms that provides specialist care in Tropical medicine and Infectious Diseases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking a Deputy Sister who is dynamic, confident, energetic, and kind to join our team and provide great quality care to our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working for the OUH in such a specialist area provides an excellent opportunity to join a multidisciplinary team and set you to a great career path.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you are interested in joining our team and would like to arrange an informal visit or discuss via phone, please contact us using the details below.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
